extendedInfo.description: This Legal Jobs application provides the latest available Legal Job listings across Australia (Segmented by Location: WA, NSW, QLD, SA, NT, VIC, TAS, ACT), the USA, UK and and Canada; curated and updated daily! What else is included: =============== * Legal Job listings for all of Australia, the USA, UK and Canada. * Career development tips and advice from career expert's Ford Myers & Brian Krueger (2 renowned International speakers) * Other daily CV and Job search tips from various sources * Interview training and advice * Plus a whole lot more to keep you at the top of your Legal career! Install this FREE Legal Jobs App Today !! P.S. New developments coming soon, including enhanced search options and more. Stay tuned!
